00:24:05.423 --> 00:24:08.884
- You got something. but not for us.
- Yes. yes. and I gotta go.

475
00:24:08.885 --> 00:24:11.512
I gotta go do that. Excuse me. Let's go.

476
00:24:11.513 --> 00:24:13.556
