560
00:28:52.835 --> 00:28:56.631
I got a gym membership
and a nutritionist. [chuckles]

561
00:28:57.465 --> 00:28:59.007
- What?
- No. it's...

562
00:28:59.008 --> 00:29:00.635
No. it's okay. You can say it.

563
00:29:02.178 --> 00:29:06.056
I guess I'm realizing
that you taking care of me

564
00:29:06.057 --> 00:29:08.518
probably got in the way
of you taking care of yourself.

565
00:29:10.144 --> 00:29:13.647
[chuckles] It's funny.
Bob says the same thing. [chuckles]

566
00:29:13.648 --> 00:29:15.941
- Bob from work?
- [both chuckle]

567
00:29:15.942 --> 00:29:18.777
You talking about me a lot
with your IRS colleagues? [chuckles]

568
00:29:18.778 --> 00:29:22.115
[chuckles] No. only the ones
who make me breakfast. [chuckles]

569
00:29:23.616 --> 00:29:25.576
Ah. Right.

570
00:29:26.619 --> 00:29:28.495
Can I. uh. can I see that?

571
00:29:28.496 --> 00:29:30.622
Oh. this is... [stutters] ...nothing.
I'm selling it.

572
00:29:30.623 --> 00:29:32.250
I-I know. I'm the one who's buying it.

573
00:29:33.418 --> 00:29:35.919
[chuckles] You listen
to <i>The Sicarius Files</i>?

574
00:29:35.920 --> 00:29:39.465
Just the last episode and you know.
I was impressed.

575
00:29:41.384 --> 00:29:44.261
And then I realized
that you met an actual serial killer

576
00:29:44.262 --> 00:29:46.346
and then I was kind of worried about you.

577
00:29:46.347 --> 00:29:50.018
So. I think I'm just trying
to make sure you're okay.

578
00:29:53.104 --> 00:29:54.438
Well. I don't know what to say.

579
00:29:54.439 --> 00:29:56.148
Say you'll give me a discount.

580
00:29:56.149 --> 00:29:58.191
Turns out my niece is a huge fan.

581
00:29:58.192 --> 00:30:01.237
so I'm trying to get
some... some cool auntie points.

582
00:30:01.863 --> 00:30:03.321
Come on.

583
00:30:03.322 --> 00:30:05.157
Look. Merino wool.

584
00:30:05.158 --> 00:30:07.118
Oh. thanks.

585
00:30:09.620 --> 00:30:10.830
Thank you.

586
00:30:11.956 --> 00:30:13.458
Wait. wait. wait. wait.

587
00:30:15.460 --> 00:30:20.380
Okay. so after the divorce.
you wanted nothing more to do with me.

588
00:30:20.381 --> 00:30:22.508
You went no contact.

589
00:30:23.718 --> 00:30:25.928
