591
00:30:29.682 --> 00:30:31.558
Who called you?

592
00:30:31.559 --> 00:30:33.895
I don't know. it was Lee something.

593
00:30:34.979 --> 00:30:37.523
- Lee Duval?
- Yeah. that's it. Do you know him?

594
00:30:38.608 --> 00:30:41.026
Yes. I do.

595
00:30:41.027 --> 00:30:43.321
Okay. Well. thanks.

596
00:30:44.906 --> 00:30:47.700
