- Jesus Christ. Okay.

605
00:31:13.851 --> 00:31:16.729
Okay. look. I had to get you a message
so that you would come and see me.

606
00:31:21.526 --> 00:31:23.861
I just wanted to say
thank you for your service.

607
00:31:28.866 --> 00:31:31.034
Well. wives are off-limits.

608
00:31:31.035 --> 00:31:34.496
Wives. children. exes.
estranged or otherwise.

609
00:31:34.497 --> 00:31:36.748
don't act like you don't know
how this works all of a sudden.

610
00:31:36.749 --> 00:31:38.459
Do you wanna hear my message?

611
00:31:40.128 --> 00:31:41.378
Okay.

612
00:31:41.379 --> 00:31:44.631
I too know what it's like
to lose the person whose respect

613
00:31:44.632 --> 00:31:46.550
you want more than anything in the world.

614
00:31:46.551 --> 00:31:50.680
I too know what it's like to want to do
anything to look better in their eyes.

615
00:31:51.222 --> 00:31:53.182
And I know how you can do that.

616
00:31:54.433 --> 00:31:55.725
What are you talking about?

617
00:31:55.726 --> 00:31:57.728
She got hooked on the podcast. didn't she?

618
00:31:58.312 --> 00:32:01.648
I wouldn't say hooked.
She was impressed. but anyway.

619
00:32:01.649 --> 00:32:03.859
it doesn't matter
because the podcast is over.

620
00:32:03.860 --> 00:32:05.110
Well. what if it's not?

621
00:32:05.111 --> 00:32:07.196
I have another message for the Fan.

622
00:32:07.864 --> 00:32:11.367
On an SD card recorded on the same phone
