693
00:36:27.790 --> 00:36:29.916
- [chuckles]
- What?

694
00:36:29.917 --> 00:36:33.336
I got good at mental math
from playing darts.

695
00:36:33.337 --> 00:36:36.047
I needed a calculator... [chuckles]
...but you're right.

696
00:36:36.048 --> 00:36:38.925
I looked for more coins and bills in case
