700
00:36:45.933 --> 00:36:47.852
I-I don't think it's that.

701
00:36:48.728 --> 00:36:51.771
We thought 1976 was about a date.

702
00:36:51.772 --> 00:36:54.649
but if he's willing to make a 20% cut

703
00:36:54.650 --> 00:36:57.652
