704
00:36:57.653 --> 00:36:59.612
he's saying something else.

705
00:36:59.613 --> 00:37:00.739
Like what?

706
00:37:00.740 --> 00:37:02.031
[JJ] Not sure.

707
00:37:02.032 --> 00:37:06.370
Sometimes a cigar is a cigar.
maybe the money is just about the money.

708
00:37:11.834 --> 00:37:13.334
I spoke with forensics.

709
00:37:13.335 --> 00:37:17.046
The brands on Lance Kingston's body
are all the same depth.

710
00:37:17.047 --> 00:37:20.508
meaning all the letters are
the same brand of typewriter.

711
00:37:20.509 --> 00:37:22.636
Penelope.
you said you had something on that.

712
00:37:25.097 --> 00:37:26.848
[snoring]

713
00:37:26.849 --> 00:37:28.726
